reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars 100% worth your money
reviews.reviewText: This dresser is actually so nice! It is very time consuming but it’s really easy to assemble I’m 13 and I did it all by myself with only my dad drilling in the screws.It fits a lot of clothes so definitely good for my shopping addiction! 100% recommend I love it so much the white is nice and has no scratches or any problems!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Easy to assemble. Nice appearance and finish. Nothing was damaged and there was no strong chemical odor that was mentioned in prior reviews. I didn't have any issues with the drawers not being in alignment. I am very pleased with this dresser for my granddaughter.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 14, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Not the sturdiest dresser, it wobbles side to side if you push on it. But I like it instructions were easy to follow I do have 2 extra pieces. It was hard to find this style of wood so I am pleased with it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for the price!
reviews.reviewText: I got this dresser put together in about an hour, its perfect for what I needed it for and the color is amazing! Drawers could be a bit bigger, but its a great buy!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Don’t recommend buying this product!
reviews.reviewText: Nice looking dresser, the instructions don’t come with words so u have to go just off pictures ,no matter how tight you put the screws the drawers just get stuck on the track, very cheap material and can easily tip over just by trying to move it (yes we tightened it the best we could without cracking the wood), the drawers don’t line up very well just overall really cheap looking and working dresser would recommend spending the extra money on something better quality, drawers also don’t come out very far Beacuse the tracks aren’t long enough, you have to constantly re position the drawer when pushing them in to get them to line up otherwise some are longer than the others, we spent hours building it and being confused by the instructions I would take it down and return it for my money back but I’ve never had good luck returning things definitely not with a big dresser so we are going to make it work till we have the money to buy a new one , definitely would not recommend buying if u have kids if they hang on it even once it will bring the dresser down it’s not very sturdy. Hope this helps I’m sorry not the best review just disappointed in the product.

reviews.reviewText: This adorable dresser exceeded my expectations! The charming design adds a whimsical touch to my child's room, and the build quality is impressive.
